flowchart TD
    A[Inbound call] --> B[Greeting: silent caller-ID lookup and welcome]
    B --> C{Business hours?}
    C -->|Open| D[Business Hours: understand request and collect details]
    C -->|Closed| E[After Hours: limited services and urgent handling]
    D --> F{Authentication required?}
    E --> F
    F -->|Yes| G[Authenticate patient]
    F -->|No - Records or new patient| H[Routing: silent destination resolution]
    G --> H
    H --> I{Scheduling?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Scheduling Init then Scheduling Engine: availability and booking]
    I -->|No| K[Transfer or Hangup: approved line only]
    J --> K
